# AI HealthGuide Project Plan and Team Management

## Foundations of AI – Assignment 3

### Project Title

AI HealthGuide: A Generative AI Assistant for Patient-Friendly Medical Communication

### Team Members

* Kulunu Hewasiliyan
* Sammy

---

# 1. Project Overview

The team has selected AI HealthGuide as the proposed project for Assignment 3.

AI HealthGuide is a Generative AI healthcare chatbot designed to help patients better understand prescriptions, medical instructions, and healthcare terminology through simplified explanations.

The project aims to improve healthcare communication and health literacy while maintaining responsible AI principles, including safety, privacy, and human oversight.

At this stage, the project concept has been finalised and planning activities have commenced.

