# 6. Planned Prototype

The team intends to develop a website-based chatbot prototype.

The prototype is expected to include:

* Homepage
* Chatbot interface
* Medical explanation examples
* Safety warnings
* User interaction workflow

The prototype will initially demonstrate chatbot functionality using simulated responses to showcase the proposed user experience and system design.

Future versions may incorporate more advanced AI functionality.

---

# 7. Risks Identified So Far

Potential project risks include:

* Limited development time
* Technical implementation challenges
* Ensuring realistic healthcare use cases
* Maintaining responsible AI principles

Mitigation strategies will be developed during later project stages.

---

